Ing '''martiliu''' (‘’hammer’’ king Ingles) kasangkapan yang pamukpuk kareng bage. Ing karaniwan a gamit na niti, ila pin deng pámukpuk [[w:nail|páku]], pamilapat kareng dake da reng gamit, ampong pamaglasak o pamangalag kareng bage. Keraklan, megawa la para king partikular a gamit deng martiliu, at miyayaliwa la tabas ampong pangabalangkas. Keraklan, bibilugan ne ning pulu o talanan ampong buntuk ing martiliu, nung nu atyu king buntuk ing keraklan king bayat na niti. Paganan ya king gamat ing pekasimpling diseniu, pero atin muring modelung de makina para kareng mangabayat a obra.

Ing maritiliu ing pekamaulagang kasangkapan kareng dakal a obra o propesion, at malyari ya muring gamitan anting [[w:war hammer|sandata]]. Mapalyaring iti ing matuang diling kasangkapan ning tau{{Fact|date=June 2007}}.

== Amlat ==
Kanita pang manga 2,400,000 BCE (maigit aduang miliung banua Bayu i Cristo), gagamitan da no reng batung miyayaliwa tabas king pamamukpuk king dutung, butul ampo kareng aliwang batu, king pamamirasu kareti, ampo king pamandukit kareti. Gagamitan da la reng batung makatuglung kareng taiktik (stick) kapamilatan da reng mangakabang pirasung balat o litid animal kanita pang atlung libung banua Bayu i Cristo (30,000 BCE) aniang libutad ning [[w:Paleolithic|Paleolithic Stone Age]]. 

== Diseniu ampong pamiyaliwa-liwa==
Ing pekamaulagang dake ning martiliu ya pin ing buntuk, metung a siksik a pirasung malyaring pamukpuk ketang bageng sukat turan, a e madidisporma.  

Deng maralas dang gagamitan a martiliu ila pin deng makatuki:
* deng martiliu da reng aluagi o karpinteru, (a gagamitan da king pamamaku), anti ing [[framing hammer]] ampo ing [[martiliung de kabra]] (claw hammer)
* [[upholstery hammer]]
* martiliung gagamitan king pamanikdong bale (construction hammers) kayabe ne ing [[masu]]
* drilling hammer - metung a masung mayan ampong makuyad talanan
* martiliung de bola (ball-peen hammer), or martiliung pang-mekaniku (mechanic’s hammer)
* cross-peen hammer, o Warrington hammer
* [[mallet]]s, including the rubber hammer and [[dead blow hammer]].
* [[Splitting maul]]
* [[stonemason's hammer]]
* [[Geologist's hammer]] o rock pick
* [[lump hammer]], o club hammer
* [[gavel]], a gagamitan da reng ukum ampong reng opisial a mamuntukan
* Tinner's Hammer

